Maintainer: Charles Mack <c.f.mack@gmail.com>
Description: When Prometheus scrapes your instance's HTTP endpoint, the client library sends the current state of all tracked metrics to the server. This R package helps collect and expect usage counters and metrics for Prometheus and containers.
